title: How to Change Your Habits & Patterns
itunes:title: How to Change Your Habits & Patterns
description:
Episode 265 -  Your habits and patterns can hold you back, but they can also push you forward if they are the correct habits and patterns. In this episode, I talk about how patterns and habits happen chemically in your brain and how to change them.
